"title": "3209: Holy Spirit, and love",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3209: holy spirit, and love",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Heartfelt concern and steadfast practical care is part of the evidence of the Holy Spirit's presence in the lives of believers.</p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's work and fruit includes the characteristic of love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22\">GAL 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">ACT 9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:30\">ROM 15:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:8\">COL 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:8-1Thess4:10\">1TH 4:8–4:10</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit fills believers with the love of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:19\">EZK 11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16-Eph3:19\">EPH 3:16–3:19</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit enables believers to live with one another in love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2-Eph4:3\">EPH 4:2–4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:6\">2CO 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:14-Gal5:16\">GAL 5:14–5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:25-Gal5:26\">GAL 5:25–5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1-Phil2:2\">PHP 2:1–2:2</a></p>\n<h2>The gift of the Holy Spirit results in practical love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31-Acts4:35\">ACT 4:31–4:35</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Love is essential in the exercise of the gifts of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:1-1Cor13:13\">1CO 13:1–13:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:1\">1CO 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:12\">1CO 14:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:26\">1CO 14:26</a></p>",
